genresAdvancedInfo.name: gospel amapiano
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Gospel Amapiano is a fusion of traditional gospel music and amapiano, a popular style of South African house music. It features the soulful vocals and uplifting lyrics of gospel music, combined with the driving beats and catchy melodies of amapiano. Gospel Amapiano has gained popularity in South Africa and beyond, and it is often played in churches and at religious events.
